<p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175515956.png" alt="1762175515956.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175515956.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">凝聚拼搏力量&nbsp;绽放青春风采我院2025年秋季运动会圆满闭幕</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">经过两天赛场角逐，我校2025年秋季运动会在全体师生的热血奔赴与全力支持中，于10月29日下午画上了圆满句点。当日，学校在操场举行运动会闭幕仪式。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>赛场掠影</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在这片燃着热血与朝气的赛场上我们撞见了一场又一场汗水与呐喊的碰撞更触摸到了青春的脉搏与热爱的滚烫让我们一同回望那些闪光的瞬间品味运动赋予青春的热烈回响</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175642424.png" alt="1762175642424.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175642424.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175664850.png" alt="1762175664850.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175664850.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175683487.png" alt="1762175683487.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175683487.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175697542.png" alt="1762175697542.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175697542.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175717507.png" alt="1762175717507.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175717507.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>荣光闪耀</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">当获奖名单揭晓，运动员脸上漾开笑意——那笑里，沾着赛场热汗，裹着训练回甘。看，短跑选手冲线的脚踝溅起胜利鼓点，跳高选手腾空撞开新高度，接力队员掌心织就默契。这些被掌声簇拥的高光时刻，是对“再撑一步”的最好加冕。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175795284.png" alt="1762175795284.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175795284.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175815560.png" alt="1762175815560.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175815560.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175831492.png" alt="1762175831492.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175831492.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175845666.png" alt="1762175845666.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175845666.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175866688.png" alt="1762175866688.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175866688.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175881299.png" alt="1762175881299.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175881299.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175896244.png" alt="1762175896244.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175896244.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175912123.png" alt="1762175912123.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175912123.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175926766.png" alt="1762175926766.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175926766.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175950216.png" alt="1762175950216.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175950216.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175967320.png" alt="1762175967320.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175967320.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175982576.png" alt="1762175982576.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762175982576.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176000495.png" alt="1762176000495.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176000495.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176020150.png" alt="1762176020150.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176020150.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176034284.png" alt="1762176034284.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176034284.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176049301.png" alt="1762176049301.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176049301.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176063673.png" alt="1762176063673.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176063673.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176077395.png" alt="1762176077395.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176077395.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>志愿护航</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">晨光微露时，“数智链”志愿服务队已在赛场旁就位；暮色漫过校园时，他们忙碌的身影仍未停歇。无论是引导方向、维持秩序，还是补位后勤，这支隐于赛事幕后的“数智链”队伍，正以无声的坚守，为每一份向前的勇气筑牢后盾，让赛场上的热烈与激昂中，始终饱含着一份温暖的力量。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176160444.png" alt="1762176160444.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176160444.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176178224.png" alt="1762176178224.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176178224.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>闭幕仪式</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176229848.png" alt="1762176229848.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176229848.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176248833.png" alt="1762176248833.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176248833.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176270513.png" alt="1762176270513.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176270513.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176292401.png" alt="1762176292401.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176292401.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176322904.png" alt="1762176322904.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1762176322904.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">经济管理学院在本届赛事中收获教职工团体积分季军、优秀组织奖、优秀新闻组织奖三项团体奖项佳绩！两天的赛场时光里，经管师生把“高效协作”的专业特质，活用到了每一场比拼里：短跑的敏捷、拔河的聚力、接力赛的默契……，把“务实敢拼”的院风刻在了赛道上。感谢每一位全力冲刺的选手，感谢每一个忙前忙后的工作人员。经济管理学院的风采，不止在报表与方案里，更在每一次并肩向前的时刻！期待下届赛场，我们再续精彩！</span></p>